title: Facebook to ban ads promoting weapon accessories, protective gear in U.S.
text: Facebook Inc said on Saturday it will ban advertisements for weapon accessories and protective equipment in the United States with immediate effect until at least two days after U.S. President-elect Joe Biden's inauguration on Jan. 20.

title: Telegram's Rapid Growth Is Bad News for Facebook's WhatsApp
text: WhatsApp's competitors are taking advantage of a rare misstep.
